[h1]Changelog[/h1]

[h2]v0.3.0 — 2026-03-18[/h2]
[b]Recursive inventory search + area safety gates[/b]

[list]
[*] Equipment checks now search equipped bags and backpacks — no need to move tools to main inventory
[*] RV Bridge actions gated by zombie proximity — greyed out when zombies are visible, chasing, or very close
[*] Timed actions cancel mid-progress if zombies appear (mirrors vanilla sleep safety)
[/list]

[h2]v0.2.0 — 2026-03-17[/h2]
[b]RV Bridge secondary extractions[/b]

[list]
[*] Secondary extraction submenu after autopsy (brain, bones, skull, teeth)
[*] Bag remains and clean table — all through the RV Bridge
[*] Table state dispatch: Empty/Corpse/Remains/Dirty with appropriate context menu options
[*] Equipment validation with tooltip builders (sack/plastics, scalpel/saw, bleach/rag)
[*] "Has Remains" table status indicator (replaces "Needs Cleaning" for post-autopsy state)
[*] 14 new translation keys for menus, tooltips, and equipment requirements
[/list]

[h2]v0.1.0 — 2026-03-17[/h2]
[b]Initial release[/b]

[list]
[*] Proximity Autopsy Table — right-click near ZVV autopsy tables and corpses for table-quality autopsies
[*] RV Bridge Remote Autopsy — use a morgue table inside your RV from outside the vehicle
[*] Morgue Table Caching — table locations persist after visiting the RV interior
[*] Table Status Indicator — colour-coded tooltip (Ready / Occupied / Needs Cleaning)
[*] 5 sandbox options for fine-tuning detection ranges and toggling features
[/list]
